issues.title: Thermal boundary inconsistencies in overlapping areas
issues.description: Thermal boundaries fail to merge consistently in retail environments with dynamic heat sources. Investigate overlapping boundary calibration.

issues.title: Anomaly detection reports redundant alerts
issues.description: During peak hours, the anomaly detection system sends duplicate alerts for minor boundary overlaps. Review redundancy filters.

commits.message: Reviewed calibration methods for merging thermal boundaries.
Added filters to reduce redundancy in anomaly detection alerts.

issues.title: Dataset labeling inconsistencies
issues.description: Certain video samples in the deepfake dataset are incorrectly labeled, causing false positives. Review and correct labels.

issues.title: Random frame skipping during model inference
issues.description: Inference pipeline occasionally skips random frames in video samples. Debug frame scheduler logic.

commits.message: Corrected mislabeled samples in deepfake dataset.
Fixed frame skipping in inference pipeline.

issues.title: False negatives in crosswalk scenarios with shadows
issues.description: Pedestrian detection model fails to detect individuals in shadowed areas of crosswalks during evening tests. Investigate shadow augmentations.

issues.title: High resource utilization during parallel camera streams
issues.description: Resource usage spikes when processing parallel camera streams in autonomous vehicle tests. Optimize resource allocation logic.

commits.message: Improved pedestrian detection in shadowed crosswalks with augmented datasets.
Optimized resource allocation for parallel camera stream processing.
